articles.title: Peek-a-boo! This is how Super Flower Blood Moon eclipse looked from space - India Today
articles.description: In a series of photographs released by the European Space Agency, the Moon can be seen playing hide and seek with one of the International Space Station's solar panels.

articles.author: New York Post
articles.title: See the Super Flower Blood Moon eclipse from around the world - New York Post
articles.description: Most of Europe, Africa and the US plus eastern Canada, New Zealand and the whole of South America, were able to see either a partial or full eclipse of the super flower blood moon on May 15.
articles.content:
Buddhist monks pray at the Sewu temple in Sleman, Yogyakarta, Indonesia, during Vesak, an annual celebration of Buddha's birth, enlightenment and death on May full moon day.
via REUTERS

articles.title: Global wheat prices hit record high after India bans exports - India Today
articles.description: After India banned wheat exports, the price of the essential commodity jumped to a record high in European trading on Monday.
